window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Jerry hits the road, fighting for life and freedom.</b><br> <br> With conspiracies at play and a Primordial revived, gathering the Prisms is more crucial than ever. Jerry must travel to find them, but enemies abound. Growing stronger is imperative. Can he do it in time?<br> <br> From a sea of clouds to a vibrant archipelago, Jerry and his friends must contend with pirates, giants, ancient wizards, and the worst opponent of all: Boney’s bone puns.</p> <p><b>Can they make it through the Archmage guarding the Archipelago? Or will they die trying—again?</b></p> <p><b>Book 2 on this laugh-fueled new slice-of-death Progression Fantasy by Valerios, bestselling author of </b><b><i>Road to Mastery</i></b><b>. Follow Jerry down his path of necromancy as he grows in power, proving his unorthodox methods may hold a lot more merit than it seems.</b></p>"; 
